        "message": "<p>Hi,</p><p>Thanks for your question. I'll get back to you within 24 hours with a detailed answer.</p><p>If it's urgent, you can also check the FAQ at behike.shop/faq.</p><br><p>— Kalani<br>Behike Support</p>",
        "options": {}
      },
